'''Truthful Toryl's Used Spaceship Lot''' was a spaceship lot on [[Tralus/Legends|Tralus]] owned by [[Toryl]] where beings could sell used and stolen ships. Han Solo attempted to sell a stolen ship there, but could only sell it as scrap due to the massive bounty on it.

